What: Exeter UFO Festival
When: Saturday, September 1, 2012 8:00 AM

Where: Exeter Town Hall
10 Front St.
Exeter, NH 03833

AN OUT OF THIS WORLD COMMUNITY
Not only is the Exeter UFO Festival an educational experience for both believers and skeptics alike, but it's a fun time for families and friends. All lectures and festival events are free of charge - no tickets needed! For schedules and information on Speakers please visit  www.exeterufofestival.com The festival will take place in Downtown Exeter, New Hampshire
Lectures will be held at Exeter Town Hall: 10 Front St, Exeter, New Hampshire
Festival activities will be held outside of Town Hall and in Founders Park.
